smartass (0.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix systemd unit ExecStart path (/opt/smartass/bin/python, not /venv/bin).
  * Fix tray: PySide6-compatible D-Bus wire format (JSON strings for complex
    returns), theme-aware Weather tab (palette roles, not hardcoded palette()),
    symbolic tray icon for dark/light theme support.
  * Feat: reactive config — Core.SetConfig now notifies running plugins and
    triggers immediate refresh; Plugin.RefreshNow added.
  * Feat: richer Weather UI — hero card, feels-like, sunrise/sunset, UV,
    precipitation, rain probability, 7-day grid with emojis and weekdays.
  * Feat: Taskfile lifecycle commands (install-service, remove-service-*).
  * Feat: GitHub Actions workflow to build on Ubuntu 22.04 / 24.04 / 25.10
    and publish releases.

 -- Saurabh Khanduja <saurabh@talonic.ai>  Wed, 22 Apr 2026 19:30:00 +0000

